txt.en: Sûhalar supplies can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should destroy Sûhalar supplies on top of the Rammas.

'I believe the Sûhalar are trying to build an encampment along the Out-wall. If you see any supplies that they have hauled up to the Rammas, destroy them. I fear another Easterling encampment so close to the North-gate could be the undoing of my post here.'
Sûhalar supplies can be found along the Rammas.\n\nYou should destroy Sûhalar supplies on top of the Rammas.
Easterlings have invaded the northern Rammas and it is up to you to see them off the Out-wall.
